title: Shakedown First Look
description:
The Arbor Shakedown is a hybrid design built to skate anything. Street, park, cruiser lines, distance, slopes.
The range of utilitarian shapes delivers true versatility with options. Size your board up for speed, down for tricks.
Find the right length and wheelbase for your stance, style, or target terrain range.
The Shakedown series comes in a Hawaiian Koa topsheet or with a Griptape top (art by Shawn McKinney)
Rider: Casey Morrow
Shakedown 33- L: 33.00" W: 8.75" WB: 15.00"
Shakedown 36- L: 36.00" W: 9.00" WB: 17.25"
Shakedown 39- L: 39.00" W: 9.25" WB: 20.50"
